A 47-year-old police inspector, Michael Ogunlade, has allegedly died during an encounter with his secret lover, (name withheld), at a hotel in Ibadan, Oyo State. Capital. CP Onadeko  “She even said the deceased was responsible for the payment of her children’s school fees for more than five years among other expenses.
  
“Where will I start again? He was my helper. My benefactor. He was like my husband because we saw him every Sunday. “Apart from once a week, the woman said the deceased always responded to anything she asked him.”